  "detailed_description": "Pixel Puzzles Junior is the perfect puzzle game for kids aged 2-5.<br><br>With 50 bright and colourful puzzles included, Pixel Puzzles Junior lets kids choose the puzzle size that's best for them. All puzzles can be played in a range of sizes, from 9, 20, 30, 42 and 56 pieces.<br><br>Avoid the mess of traditional jigsaw puzzles and let the kids play their puzzles digitally.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A range of sizes from 9 to 56 pieces.<br></li><li>Perfect for ages 2 - 5.<br></li><li>Bright cartoon puzzle images.<br></li><li>Colorful puzzling atmosphere.<br></li><li>Auto Saving, never lose progress.<br></li><li>Traditional puzzle gameplay.<br></li><li>Interactive play environment.</li></ul>",
